{"tid":1017592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"健力士銷量紀錄 史上最成功遊戲主機 -- PS2","createTime":"2019-02-11T14:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T02:06:38.000Z","uid":25345,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"42ae33b9269f960f20edb7b48086abe4f701a922","tid":1017592,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/1c/PS2-Versions.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F1%2F1c%2FPS2-Versions.jpg&h=3a95046e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.catawiki.nl/assets/2018/1/6/b/c/0/bc0bb15e-a1d6-40ed-ae5e-41e9d5c92496.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.catawiki.nl%2Fassets%2F2018%2F1%2F6%2Fb%2Fc%2F0%2Fbc0bb15e-a1d6-40ed-ae5e-41e9d5c92496.jpg&h=0918f9bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2016年3月31日，PS2 平台上《最終幻想11》的線上服務正式關閉。4月2日索尼正式宣佈，PS2遊戲的所有線上服務現在已經全部結束。這也意味着於2000年3月4日推出PlayStation 2（簡稱PS2）正式落幕！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2012年11月3日，索尼官方正式宣佈停產PS2。2012年12月28日，PS2在日本地區正式停止出貨。截止2012年2月，PS2已經在全球銷售超過1億5千萬台（包括超薄版等），屢次被票選為史上最優秀遊戲主機。同時也是有史以來最流行的遊戲機，它還是以較大的優勢擊敗了另一個企圖超越它競爭對手NDS。PS2平台上一共推出了超過10萬款遊戲，2011年PS2主機上的全部遊戲銷量已經超過了15億份。<br />\n<br />\nPS2還有一個很偉大的功績便是對DVD普及作出的貢獻，PS2是第一個搭載DVD播放功能的家庭用娛樂終端，對DVD普及做出了巨大貢獻。發賣至今已經踏入第2012年，在以東歐、中東、東南亞、南美為中心的地區仍然有一定需求,就像網友說的：PS1普及了CD，PS2普及了DVD，PS3普及了藍光，未來PS4普及VR。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n16年時間PS2拿下四個遊戲歷史中無法超越的記錄：公司支持時間最長、世界上銷售時間最長、世界最暢銷以及擁有遊戲陣容最豐富的主機。"},{"pid":"b9a530aec91eef16e2feb9c3be1d9df983a1a5f4","tid":1017592,"uid":51200,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:17:08.000Z","msg":"真心，千禧之後<br />\n<br />\nPs2第一<br />\n其他再爭<br />\nGameboy NDS Xbox360 wii"},{"pid":"1c945fa9da4844cdce745f5a72bcd4ddc6bb6f18","tid":1017592,"uid":174191,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:20:31.000Z","msg":"發賣至今已經踏入第2012年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61579c959b424d92c2b6ae8124693d16a8513050","tid":1017592,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:26:24.000Z","msg":"咁究竟之後嗰三千萬賣咗去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d1790f0905c4aa69b4a52c42a52c9c32241735","tid":1017592,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"永恆經典"},{"pid":"ae4de2cad5d2a9eb0099506476533cca2dc09620","tid":1017592,"uid":139606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:27:46.000Z","msg":"Mein Fuirher"},{"pid":"a8663f8b457e3d3ee7670420b2e44bc466373579","tid":1017592,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:29:24.000Z","msg":"ps2畫面吊打ps4"},{"pid":"8577e0e2ef8d45af6c069b347be1cb8512477480","tid":1017592,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b9a530aec91eef16e2feb9c3be1d9df983a1a5f4","tid":1017592,"uid":51200,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:17:08.000Z","msg":"真心，千禧之後<br />\n<br />\nPs2第一<br />\n其他再爭<br />\nGameboy NDS Xbox360 wii"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:31:48.000Z","msg":"銷量嚟講nds&gt;&gt;&gt;gb&gt;&gt;wii&gt;xb360"},{"pid":"12fbd8aaf26e449015b2d8a1fefd6bec7b5ae2f2","tid":1017592,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"ps2個外形<br />\n依家來看都係一流"},{"pid":"ff7355bdac93236c7a1ae674aa6df0941ce51d55","tid":1017592,"uid":180188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12fbd8aaf26e449015b2d8a1fefd6bec7b5ae2f2","tid":1017592,"uid":191926,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"ps2個外形<br />\n依家來看都係一流"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"仲有岩岩開機個下聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162293b2030c249777ce6dc96b0a72da30114e84","tid":1017592,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"12fbd8aaf26e449015